        "content": "<p>I wonder if it would be nice to modify <code>calc</code> syntax to let you write <code>;</code> instead of <code>:= ?_</code>. It's a lot less visually noisy, though it probably causes conflicts with <code>by</code> notation's semicolons.</p>",
